<HEAD>Lenin Mausoleum in Red Square to Close for Maintenance</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MOSCOW (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Lenin's tomb in Red Square will be closed for two
months beginning in November for essential maintenance, Tass said
Monday.
   The mausoleum will be closed from Nov. 10 to Jan. 15, 1990, the
brief announcement from the Kremlin commandant's office said.
   The red granite tomb draws thousands of visitors daily, both
