<TEXT>
   Actor-comedian Chevy Chase was
released Monday from a hospital, where he was taken Sunday after
complaining of chest pains during a benefit tennis tournament in
nearby Boca Raton.
   Chase, 46, was taken to Delray Community Hospital after
apparently suffering heat exhaustion during a practice round with
